The paper deals with explainability of deep neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the umbrella of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of game-theoretic notions and the validation on text and image datasets suggest that the paper is also relevant to machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and information retrieval (cs.IR).
